Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.35,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Defining lines between the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.89,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And what will soon become the prey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.27,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I've giving up on counting blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:21.06,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The gods can judge me when I'm dead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.44,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Cause I can not take this anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:27.49,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'm done with the feelings that I've known in paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.95,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Lost in paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.37,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The feeling of hatred burns my soul
